:title Connection Settings
:label connection settings

Configuration of the connection.

* <<basic settings|Basic Settings>>
. Basic settings, max. retry count, max connections per server, proxy configuration, user agent and bandwidth limit.
* <<authentication settings|Authentication Settings>>
. Authentication settings for websites with standard http authentication. 
* <<cookie settings|Cookie Settings>>
. Configuration of the cookies which are sent when opening an connection to an http server.
* <<http response|Http Response Behaviour>>
. Defines the behaviour for certain HTTP Status Codes.
